  "lastUpdatedOn": "2012-10-17",
  "religion": "Lima is a devout Catholic.",
  "politicalViews": "Lima's religion dictates her stance on social issues, but no word on much else.",
  "author": "Tom Kershaw",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0992596/bio",
      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Lima – Biography.",
      "text": "Adriana Lima was born and raised in Salvador, Brazil. She moved to New York City at 16 to pursue her modeling career."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://waitingtillmarriage.org/adriana-lima-waited-until-age-27/",
      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Lime – Virgin Until Age 27",
      "text": "Lima is a strict Catholic who goes to Mass every week and, unless doing a photo shoot or show, wears a scapular (a Catholic necklace of sorts) around her neck at all times."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0506/17/sbt.01.html",
      "sourceTitle": "Transcripts",
      "text": "I can't tell if she was actually a nun at one point or only aspired to be,"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "but being a nun had something to do with her upbringing."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://waitingtillmarriage.org/adriana-lima-waited-until-age-27/",
      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Lime – Virgin Until Age 27",
      "text": "She is so devoted to her faith, Adriana supposedly abstained from sex until she was married at the age of 27."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "She said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.gq.com/women/photos/200603/adriana-lima-virgin-underwear-model",
      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Lime: Our Favorite… Virgin?",
      "text": "Sex is for after marriage… [Men] have to respect that this is my choice. If there's no respect, that means they don't want me."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0992596/bio",
      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Lima – Biography.",
      "text": "That's rough news for hopeful, hormone-driven men the world over considering Lima has been rated the world's most desirable woman over and over and over by various hotness-rating entities."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0992596/bio",
      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Lima – Biography.",
      "text": "Not that it matters. Lima was married in 2009."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": "Politics of a hyper-religious international supermodel"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.gq.com/women/photos/200603/adriana-lima-virgin-underwear-model",
      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Lime: Our Favorite… Virgin?",
      "text": "Politically, Lima hasn't given us much to go on. She did say she believes of the teachings of the Catholic Church. She said, very clearly, that she thinks abortion is a crime for example."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "But that would also include: no birth control, no divorce and no gay marriage (among other things). If she was American, you could imagine her being a staunch supporter of the likes of Rick Santorum. She'd probably be quite the hot little conservative."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0992596/bio",
      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Lima – Biography.",
      "text": "Lima is an international woman. Born and raised in Brazil, career in the U.S. and now married to a Serbian. Lima applied for Serbian citizenship,"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.rantrave.com/Rave/Adriana-Lima-Fell-In-Love-With-Serbia.aspx",
      "sourceTitle": "Rave – Adriana Lime Fell In Love With Serbia",
      "text": "saying she loved the Balkan nation."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "From what I've seen, people whose lives are so multinational go one of two ways: take a meta-political, geopolitical approach to the world, or they don't care too much. I'd imagine Lima would fall into the latter category."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0992596/bio",
      "sourceTitle": "Adriana Lima – Biography.",
      "text": "She does do quite a bit of charity work for orphans and the less fortunate in her home country of Brazil."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "But that's not politics, that's just uncontroversial charity."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    }
  ],
